Package control.shop_items

Class Item

java.lang.Object
control.shop_items.Item
public class Item extends Object
This class represents an item in an online store. The item has a name, description, image, brand, unitType, itemStatus, and price.
Author:
Maya Ayman, Mohamed Essam
